This is the beginnings of an install document, mainly aimed at people
developing/assisting with exordium.

To compile exordium using the sources found on the CVS repository, you will
be required to have the following installed (in the following order):

  Software          | Version         | URL
 -------------------+-----------------+---------------------------------------
  GNU GCC           | 3.x series      | http://www.gnu.org/software/gcc/
  GNU m4            | 1.4 or later    | http://www.gnu.org/software/m4/
  GNU Autoconf      | 2.57 or later   | http://www.gnu.org/software/autoconf/
  Perl              | 5.6 or later    | http://www.perl.com/
  GNU Automake      | 1.7.3 or later  | http://www.gnu.org/software/automake/
  GNU Guile Library | 1.6 or later    | http://www.gnu.org/software/guile/
  GNU Autogen       | 5.5.3 or later  | http://www.gnu.org/software/autogen/
  LibAISutil        | 1.1 or later    | http://www.sf.net/projects/libais/
  KineIRCd          | SS 200303260939 | http://www.sf.net/projects/kineircd/
